"use client" import type React from "react" import { useState, useEffect, useCallback } from "react" import { Link } from "react-router-dom" import { useAuth } from "../../contexts/AuthContext" import { apiService } from "../../services/api" import type { Skill, Order } from "../../types" import { toast } from "react-toastify" interface DashboardData { skills: Skill[] orders: Order[] stats: { total_skills: number total_orders: number total_points: number pending_orders: number } } const Dashboard: React.FC = () => { const { user } = useAuth() const [data, setData] = useState(null) const [loading, setLoading] = useState(true) const fetchDashboardData = useCallback(async () => { try { const [skills, orders, profile] = await Promise.all([ apiService.getSkills(), apiService.getOrders(), apiService.getProfile(), ]) const userSkills = skills.filter((skill: Skill) => skill.provider === user?.id) const userOrders = orders.filter((order: Order) => order.buyer === user?.id || order.skill?.provider === user?.id) setData({ skills: userSkills, orders: userOrders, stats: { total_skills: userSkills.length, total_orders: userOrders.length, total_points: profile.points || 0, pending_orders: userOrders.filter((order: Order) => order.status === "pending").length, }, }) } catch (error) { console.error("Error fetching dashboard data:", error) toast.error("حدث خطأ في تحميل بيانات لوحة التحكم") } finally { setLoading(false) } }, [user?.id]) useEffect(() => { fetchDashboardData() }, [fetchDashboardData]) if (loading) { return (

جاري تحميل لوحة التحكم...

) } return (
